Package redecker.mickey.webcnc.types

Class Switch

java.lang.Object
redecker.mickey.webcnc.types.Switch
public class Switch extends Object
This class represents a TSN capable switch with a unique identifier, its SNMP credentials, its TSN ports, and network system name information about itself and neighbors that were gathered via LLDP by the switch
Author:
Mickey Redecker

  • Constructor Details

    • Switch

      public Switch(String switchIdentifier, String address, Integer port, String sysname, List<String> neighborSysNames, List<String> neighborPortIds, List<Integer> neighborLocalPorts, String authUserName, AuthAlgorithm authAlgorithm, String authPassword, EncryptionAlgorithm encryptAlgorithm, String encryptPassword, List<Port> TSNPorts, boolean isReachable)
      Parameters:
      switchIdentifier - a unique identifier
      address - The IP address of the switch
      port - The UDPÃœ port of the switch
      sysname - The switches system name
      neighborSysNames - A list of system names of the switches neighbor devices, list position must match local port and port id
      neighborPortIds - A list of port ids (usually MAC Adresses) of the switches neighbor devices, list position must match local port and sysname
      neighborLocalPorts - A list of the switches port numbers to which the switches neighbor devices are connected, list position must match sysnames and port id
      authUserName - the SNMPv3 authentication user name
      authAlgorithm - the SNMPv3 authentication algorithm
      authPassword - the SNMPv3 authentication password
      encryptAlgorithm - the SNMPv3 encryption Algorithm
      encryptPassword - the SNMPv3 encryption password
      TSNPorts - a list of TSN-capable Ports of the switch
      isReachable - Indicates whether the switch is reachable or not
